                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.3.7:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                                    - Setups tab: Car names have the year added.<LineBreak/>
                                    - Setups tab: Added button to right click menu to open car directory.<LineBreak/>
                                    - Setups tab: Added button to browser tab to refresh the setup list.<LineBreak/>
                                    - Setup conversion added: Lamborghini Huracán GT3 2015, Nissan GT-R Nismo GT3 2015, Ferrari 488 GT3 2018.<LineBreak/>
                                    - Livery Importer: Added 1 file filter for all supported types.<LineBreak/>
                                    - Livery Importer: Add strategy for botched archives (containing no separate folders).
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.3.6:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                                    - About tab: When a new release is available a new button allows you to visit the latest release and download the newest version.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.3.5:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
