                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.3.4:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                                    - Added Bulk DDS Generator: Got many skins without dds files? this will generate the dds files. Sit back and relax.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.3.3:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                                    - Livery browser: added two tabs for grouping style, Car model type and Teams.<LineBreak/>
                                    - Livery viewer: fix crash when generating dds files.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.3.2:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                                    - Fuel calcalator: added button to fetch data from game.<LineBreak/>
                                    - Livery browser: fix for fetching the liveries to display them in the list.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.3.1:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                                    - Telemetry: Display Array data.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.3.0:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                                    - Add Telemetry tab, very basic for now, might still have some data bugs, also not all data is shown as data yet.<LineBreak/>
                                    - Add car model name to livery viewer.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.10:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Add features panel to about tab.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.9:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Setup conversion added: Bentley Continental GT3 2018, Lamborghini Huracán GT3 Evo, Lexus RC F GT3, Nissan GT-R Nismo GT3 2018.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.8:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Added exception handling so the manager will not crash for windows version lower than 11.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.7:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Livery exporter: Added skin pack exporter, right click teams or skins to add.<LineBreak/>
                            - ACC Manager Folder: Added dedicated folder for the acc Manager, My Documents/ACC Manager.<LineBreak/>
                            - Added logger which logs to the dedicated folder/Log.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.6:
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Icon: Something not too fancy, but it shows what the tool does.<LineBreak/>
                            - Setup conversion: fixed Porsche 911 II GT3.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.5
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Livery Displayer: Added button to generate dds files..<LineBreak/>
                            - Livery Exporter: Now includes dds files if available.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.4
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Livery Displayer: Added buttons to open livery json and livery folder.<LineBreak/>
                            - Livery Displayer: Added nationality, Paint materials for body and rims.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.3
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Add setup conversion for: Mercedes-AMG GT3 2020, BMW M4 GT3, Ferrari 488 GT3 Evo.<LineBreak/>
                            - Fuel calculator: fixed fuel value parsing when windows language is set differently.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.2
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Livery exporter: exported zips are now according to acc folder structure.<LineBreak/>
                            - Livery exporter: export team with all the skins inside in a single zip.<LineBreak/>
                            - Livery importer: added support for archives with multiple liveries.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.1
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Livery Browser: Skins are grouped by team name.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,0">
                                <TextBlock 
                           Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignBody1TextBlock}"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="Wrap" >
                            0.0.2.0
                                </TextBlock>
                                <TextBlock Style="{StaticResource MaterialDesignDataGridTextColumnStyle}" HorizontalAlignment="Left" TextWrapping="WrapWithOverflow">
                            - Add Livery Browser, displays: team name, display name, car number, decals image and sponsors image.<LineBreak/>
                            - Add Livery exporter: right click livery to save as zip.<LineBreak/>
                            - Add Livery importer: supports (.7z, .rar, .zip), can import multiple archives at once, though multiple liveries per archive is not supported.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

