                            - Add setup conversion for: Audi R8 LMS evo II(by Jubka), Honda NSX GT3 Evo, Mclaren 720S GT3, Porsche II GT3 R.
                                </TextBlock>
                            </StackPanel>

                            <StackPanel Margin="0,10,0,10">
